column2:
"Excellent. I see you're one of the good ones.
My fears were completely unfounded, then."

"Sending Thumbs-up is a tradition
that keeps morale up at both ends."

"Heh. Speaking of morale, that reminds me
of this one time, in the old days..."

"うむ、よろしい！
やはり君は優秀なアークスだな。
杞憂で済んでよかった。"

"グッジョブの送信とは
お互いがお互いに笑顔になる
素晴らしい行為だと思うぞ！"
